title: [Balmy Blooms, Nook]
description: The regressed nook is accented throughout with lush, jewel-toned flowers and vibrant green herbs.  A narrow grey stone bench wreathes around the perimeter of the room, highlighting a centrally placed woven silk tapestry of a sprawling elm tree with wide-arching branches.
